## Unsettable type

Extracts unsettable properties from a type

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type Unsettable<T> = string & Exclude<{
    [K in keyof T]: T extends Record<K, T[K]> ? never : K;
}[keyof T], undefined>;
```
